articles.title: Returning to his old home, Stefon Diggs is the pivotal Patriot in their biggest win in years
articles.description:
A week after his finest game as a Patriot, with six catches for 101 yards in a 42-13 rout of the Panthers, Diggs relegated that performance to distant runner-up status.

The post Returning to his old home, Stefon Diggs is the pivotal Patriot in their biggest win in years appeared first on Boston.com.
